Freaky girl, Libra sign, I know how you get when the stars align 🎂

There is no way to put into words the absolute heart ache and agony you leaving this earth has caused. There will forever be a gaping hole in mine, and everyone’s heart that will always be filled with the fierce love we feel for you everyday. There is literally not a single 24 hour day that goes by that I am not effected by your absence. Losing someone so young and vivacious is one of the worlds greatest tragedy’s and we were deprived of everything you had to offer to this world. You were, and still are, the most radiant soul I will ever meet in this lifetime. Your pure and genuine heart was recognized by everyone you came in contact with. You exuded the most gorgeous energy I’ve ever been surrounded with and I will always cherish and thank god for the time we got to spend together. I pray you are looking over me, and are proud of me, as I consider your blessing in everything I do in this life, and for the rest of it. It is difficult to accept it’s been a year since we lost you, and it has only gotten harder as I go through life so desperate to be able to share it with you. I will do everything to keep your memory and spirit alive and include you in everything I do. To the ends of this earth I love you and miss you, and I can’t wait to meet you again someday Eric.
